**_Fellowships, awards, and recognitions_**   
- **2019-2020**: Mitacs Canadian Science Policy Fellowship, Victoria, BC, Canada     
- **2019**: Third [place](https://www.uvic.ca/research/centres/biomedical/events-outreach/health-and-regenerative-medicine-hackathon/index.php) for designing prosthetic hand tools at Health and Regenerative Medicine Hackathon (donation of award to Victoria Hand Project)   
- **2019**: BC Premier’s award nominee in evidence-based design using integrated data, Government of BC, Finalist Team    
- **2019**: Innovative project proposal recognition at Vancouver Island's Code.Hack hackathon  
- **2018 & 2019**: Travel and team lead award to attend Hackseq Genomics Hackathon in Vancouver, BC organized by UBC/Hackseq  
- **2018-2019**: Mitacs Canadian Science Policy [Fellowship](https://github.com/NoushinN/noushinn.github.io/blob/master/images/cspf_certificate.pdf), Victoria, BC, Canada   
- **2018**: Health and Regenerative Medicine Hackathon in kind value in mentorship award organized by University of Victoria  
- **2018**: Entrepreneurship training at e@UBC and in kind value in mentorship   
- **2018**: Mini-MBA award, Partnership with Graduate Management Consulting Association at UBC  
- **2017**: Travel award to attend the American Association of Cancer Research conference in Washington DC   
- **2016-2017**: Rare Genomics Institute’s BeHEARD Technology [Prize](https://blog.addgene.org/supporting-rare-disease-research-with-beheard-2017), partnership with addgene  
- **2016-2017**: Amazon Web Services Cloud Research Grant, Award No. 129870357408    
- **2015-2017**: Mitacs Accelerate Postdoctoral Fellowship [Award](https://www.mitacs.ca/sites/default/files/uploads/page/mitacs_annual_report_for_innovation_science_and_economic_development_canada_2016-17.pdf)   
- **2014-2015**: American Society for Microbiology Science teaching award    
- **2012-2013**: Siebel Stem Cell Institute [Fellowship](https://reeis.usda.gov/web/crisprojectpages/0218571-molecular-mechanism-of-dietary-restrictions-protection-against-aging-and-diseases-of-aging.html), University of California Berkeley  
- **2012**: Travel award from the University of California Berkeley to attend Stem Cell Retreat in Asilomar, CA    
- **2010**: Graduate Student Research Award, University of Toronto Scarborough   
- **2009**: Natural Sciences and Engineering Research Council [(NSERC)-CGS](https://csmb-scbm.ca/uploads/Final2010-2011Bulletin.pdf)  
- **2009**: Travel award from Connective Tissue Conference (CCTC) to attend the annual meeting in Calgary, AB    
- **2008**: Travel award from Connective Tissue Conference (CCTC) to attend the annual meeting in Montreal, QC          
- **2008**: General Motors Women in Science and Mathematics Award   
- **2007**: Travel award from Connective Tissue Conference (CCTC) to attend the annual meeting in Halifax, NS            
- **2007**: Travel award from American Society for Cell Biology (ASCB) to attend the annual meeting in San Diego, CA   
- **2006-2010**: Let's Talk Science honorable mention and recognition for contribution to science and education   


 